<bioghist altrender="history" encodinganalog="545" id="a2">
	<head>Historical Note</head>
	<p>The town of Danbury was settled in 1685, named in October 1687 and incorporated as a town in May 1702. The City of Danbury was incorporated in 1889. The town and city consolidated on January 1, 1965.
</p>
</bioghist>

<scopecontent encodinganalog="520" id="a3">
	<head>Scope and Content</head>
	<p>Tax and town welfare records for the town of Danbury.
</p>
</scopecontent>
